01:01:03,231 --> 01:01:04,964
Something's intercepting
our signal.

841
01:01:05,098 --> 01:01:06,998
[♪♪♪]

842
01:01:10,765 --> 01:01:12,365
[GROANS]

843
01:01:12,498 --> 01:01:14,198
You murdered my wife.

844
01:01:16,132 --> 01:01:17,266
[GROANING]

845
01:01:19,832 --> 01:01:22,666
Your wife?
