01:02:44,440 --> 01:02:46,872
a lot more than it's gonna...
Ah, whatever.

871
01:02:47,006 --> 01:02:48,573
[ELECTRICAL CRACKLING]

872
01:02:48,707 --> 01:02:50,506
[YELLING]

873
01:02:52,940 --> 01:02:55,207
[LAUGHING]

874
01:02:55,341 --> 01:02:57,873
- [RAY GRUNTS]
- [YELLS, WHIMPERS]

