981
01:07:55,666 --> 01:07:58,332
Oh, I am so clever.
I don't want that.

982
01:07:58,466 --> 01:08:01,065
Right. Oh, here it is. Bingo.

983
01:08:03,033 --> 01:08:06,367
No! No! Not that one.
That won't work.

984
01:08:06,500 --> 01:08:09,500
Trust me. Here, follow me.
And take this.

985
01:08:09,633 --> 01:08:11,966
